description: Amundi STOXX Europe 600 Healthcare UCITS ETF Acc seeks to replicate as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the STOXX Europe 600 Healthcare Net Total Return Index (the "Index"), denominated in euros, while minimizing the volatility of the difference between the return of the Sub-Fund and the return of the Benchmark Index (the "Tracking Error"). The expected Tracking Error under normal market conditions is 1%. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi STOXX Europe 600 Healthcare UCITS ETF Acc
